# Changelog

## 1.0.0 — 2026-06-14

- Initial public release.
- Configurable colored window frames for Cinnamon.
- Rule matching by title, class, instance and window type.
- Separate active and inactive colors.
- Adjustable frame width, corner radius, opacity, glow and edge offsets.
- Per-rule frame width and corner radius.
- Live configuration reload.
- Graphical GTK 3 configurator.
- Default rules for local terminals, SSH hosts and root shells.
